--- !u!114 &1526194004
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1526194002}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 21c947034056e3347adb5064ad3e223f, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::TutorialController
  steps:
  - title: Game Objective
    description: Use your dice and jokers to beat the score on the top left corner
      to clear that section and go on a next section.End of a section you get a certain
      money, you can use them in shop to buy joker or dice and continue. Until you
      fail.
    visual: {fileID: -2586578413341101539, guid: 694b1ea5ff216c64bbc1c72d384b6e9b, type: 3}
  - title: Jokers
    description: Jokers are one time usable coins. There are 4 types of joker by
      rarity; common, uncommon, rare, legendary
    visual: {fileID: 6616785686708724065, guid: 7bbf0a89a7d7e18469e5fe6d91485f1d, type: 3}
  - title: Jokers
    description: Each Joker has unique effect on dice, points, or to  ingame mechanics.
    visual: {fileID: -4977956782725488155, guid: 7acaeb691d9048040aa61285c065d623, type: 3}
  - title: Forge
    description: In Shop you can forge on to your dice to a special ability that
      gives you advantage.
    visual: {fileID: -1748509332933103347, guid: 4f1b7b034f731e949a381f15a5ed1756, type: 3}
  - title: Rigged Dice
    description: 'In Shop there is a section that you can buy a dice. In certain
      chance you can get a rigged dice. '
    visual: {fileID: -2014721329905436536, guid: 73c6555f253c1de4ab0251e4c1c552ec, type: 3}
  - title: Rigged Dice
    description: 'In Shop there is a section that you can buy a dice. In certain
      chance you can get a rigged dice. '
    visual: {fileID: -2014721329905436536, guid: 73c6555f253c1de4ab0251e4c1c552ec, type: 3}
  - title: Tickets
    description: 'When you clear boss section for first time it gives you a ticket.
      You can use that in startup menu to buy some startups. Every boss section gives
      you only one ticket and can not be redemied for the other playthroughs. '
    visual: {fileID: -7606890647880417450, guid: 3fc3dff4b88d49348a579ec7c0d82d05, type: 3}
  - title: Startups
    description: With tickets you can buy some advantages for your run. This advantages
      are permanent. And you can equip only 3 of them for your run. If you want to
      reset your progress you can use the reset button on the top right.
    visual: {fileID: 5501877385742170255, guid: 701a7cec45bca0a4aa81a64f3f4621c8, type: 3}
  - title: Synergy
    description: Use the synergy of dice and jokers to blow up the scores. Good Luck!
    visual: {fileID: -6731717548956466261, guid: 452349ad15d957f4cab2cc459369e9ad, type: 3}
  tutorialPanel: {fileID: 96547621}
  displayImage: {fileID: 77501818}
  titleText: {fileID: 1584434220}
  descriptionText: {fileID: 1103353164}
  pageCounterText: {fileID: 786343585}
  nextButton: {fileID: 899547357}
  prevButton: {fileID: 1519222589}
  closeButton: {fileID: 2044140673}
